;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17656,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/20\/beware-luxury\/","url_meta":{"origin":36959,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Extravagance: Believers do not live a life of luxury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, sent him to Yemen and he said, \u201cBeware of luxury, for the servants of Allah do not live luxuriously.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 22105 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0630\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":391,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/20\/rights-allah-tawheed\/","url_meta":{"origin":36959,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Monotheism: Rights of Allah upon His servants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 20, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu'adh bin Jabal reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"O Mu'adh, do you know what the right of Allah is upon His servants?\" I said, \"Allah and His Messenger know best.\" The Prophet said, \"To worship Him alone and to associate none in worship with Him.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&q